类 PositionGoalTarget

it.polimi.ingsw.model.PositionGoalTarget
所有已实现的接口:
Serializable
public class PositionGoalTarget extends TargetCard implements Serializable
Represents a PositionGoalTarget in the game, which extends TargetCard. A PositionGoalTarget has properties such as two required elements and a corner position.

    • checkGoal

      public int checkGoal(Board board)
      Checks the goal of the PositionGoalTarget based on the specified board. This method calculates how many complete sets of two elements can be formed in a specific corner position on the board.
      指定者:
      checkGoal 在类中 TargetCard

    • countPoint

      public int countPoint(Board board)
      Counts the points scored by the PositionGoalTarget based on the specified board. Points are calculated as the base points of the card multiplied by the number of complete sets achieved.
